{"article_id":"0LQSPOI8ctGckooI","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Charles E. Grassley said Thursday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"the FBI ' s updated background report doesn ' t provide any new evidence","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to corroborate the allegations of sexual misconduct against Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Mr. Grassley , the Iowa Republican in charge","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"of shepherding Judge Kavanaugh ' s nomination ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"there ' s \" no hint of misconduct \"","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"after a dayslong review of allegations of sexual assault at a high school party ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"made by Christine Blasey Ford ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"or that the judge exposed himself at a college party ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"made by Deborah Ramirez .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"\" These uncorroborated accusations have been unequivocally and repeatedly rejected by Judge Kavanaugh ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"and neither the Judiciary Committee nor the FBI could locate any third parties","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"who can attest to any of the allegations , \"","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"The report was finalized overnight","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"and senators were getting their first look at it Thursday morning .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Anti-Kavanaugh activists were not swayed by the lack of corroboration in the report .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Hundreds mobbed the office buildings in the Capitol complex Thursday afternoon","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"loudly demanding senators vote against the judge .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"U.S. Capitol Police officers were escorting some protesters out in handcuffs .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Senators , meanwhile , were taking turns","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"looking at the single copy of the FBI ' s report ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"held in a special secure room .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh ' s nomination to the Supreme Court has been held up","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"while senators debate the allegations about decades-old partying and sexual improprieties .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"The issue has been compounded by the judge ' s admitted affinity for beer .","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"Democrats complained","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"the report did not include interviews with Ms. Blasey Ford nor with Judge Kavanaugh themselves .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"They said","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"the FBI seemed to have been ordered to limit its review .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"\" The most notable part of this report is what ' s not in it , \"","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"said Sen. Dianne Feinstein , the top Democrat on the Judiciary Committee .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford gave compelling testimony last week about a party in 1982","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"where she says","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh groped her ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"tried to strip off her clothes","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"and stifled her cries for help .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"But none of the witnesses","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"she identified","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"as being at the party","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"have been able to corroborate her story ,","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"and there is no contemporaneous evidence","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"to back her up .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"Democrats said","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"without talking to Ms. Blasey Ford","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"or seeing her documents ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"including therapy notes and a polygraph exam","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"she arranged to take in August ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"investigators aren ' t getting the full picture .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"Democrats ' leader , Sen. Charles E. Schumer ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"who said","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"he had been briefed on the report ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"he disagreed with Mr. Grassley ' s assertion","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"that the FBI found no evidence of any problems with the judge ' s past .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"He would not divulge","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"what he meant by that ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"but said","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"he wanted to see a redacted version of the report made public .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"\" Why shouldn ' t all of America see the facts ? \"","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Republicans , though , said","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"they trusted the FBI to follow the leads","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"it thought best .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham , South Carolina Republican , emerged from his briefing on the report","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"to say","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"the FBI talked with 10 new witnesses","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"and had whatever latitude","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"it needed .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"the information , particularly from Leland Keyser , a longtime Blasey Ford friend","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"who","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"she says","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"was at the party","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"where the assault happened ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"\" reinforced \" Judge Kavanaugh ' s vehement denials .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":109,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":100,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":93,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":91,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":79,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par